{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853408860,"sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","part":{"id":"prt_d791c8657001sLgWCM0tgK2WBU","messageID":"msg_d791c6724001332brpKN7Ig0AR","sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/notes.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/notes.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 Notes\n2: \n3: ## Implementation Notes\n4: \n5: ### Controller-Runtime Version\n6: \n7: Use controller-runtime v0.20.x which aligns with Kubernetes 1.32+.\n8: \n9: ### Key Dependencies\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: import (\n13:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager\"\n14:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\"\n15:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/controller\"\n16:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/handler\"\n17:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/source\"\n18:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\"\n19: )\n20: ```\n21: \n22: ### Reconcile Result Patterns\n23: \n24: - Return `reconcile.Result{Requeue: true}` for transient errors\n25: - Return `reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: duration}` for backoff\n26: - Return `reconcile.Result{}` for successful completion\n27: - Return error for retry with exponential backoff\n28: \n29: ### Finalizer Naming Convention\n30: \n31: Use `\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/finalizer\"` as the finalizer name.\n32: \n33: ## References\n34: \n35: - [controller-runtime Documentation](https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n36: - [Kubebuilder Book - CronJob Tutorial](https://book.kubebuilder.io/cronjob-tutorial/cronjob-tutorial)\n37: - [Kubernetes Controller Guidelines](https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/sig-api-machinery/controllers.md)\n\n(End of file - total 37 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007 Notes\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Controller-Runtime Version\n\nUse controller-runtime v0.20.x which aligns with Kubernetes 1.32+.\n\n### Key Dependencies\n\n```go\nimport (\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/manager\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/reconcile\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/controller\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/handler\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/source\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\"\n)\n```","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/notes.md","time":{"start":1775853408840,"end":1775853408858}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853408862,"sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","part":{"id":"prt_d791c8c80001JCVQCzQzaBj1li","messageID":"msg_d791c6724001332brpKN7Ig0AR","sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/plan.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/plan.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 Implementation Plan\n2: \n3: ## Phase 1: Controller Foundation\n4: \n5: - [ ] Set up controller-runtime manager\n6: - [ ] Configure scheme with AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter types\n7: - [ ] Implement basic controller structure\n8: - [ ] Add health checks and metrics setup\n9: \n10: ## Phase 2: Resource Watchers\n11: \n12: - [ ] Implement AgentRuntime resource watcher\n13: - [ ] Implement CodeInterpreter resource watcher\n14: - [ ] Configure event filters (generation, deletion timestamp)\n15: - [ ] Add watch predicates for relevant changes only\n16: \n17: ## Phase 3: Reconcile Loop\n18: \n19: - [ ] Implement AgentRuntime reconciler\n20: - [ ] Implement CodeInterpreter reconciler\n21: - [ ] Add request queue with workqueue\n22: - [ ] Implement rate limiting configuration\n23: \n24: ## Phase 4: Finalizer Management\n25: \n26: - [ ] Add finalizer for AgentRuntime resources\n27: - [ ] Add finalizer for CodeInterpreter resources\n28: - [ ] Implement finalizer handler for graceful deletion\n29: - [ ] Handle cleanup before finalizer removal\n30: \n31: ## Phase 5: Status Management\n32: \n33: - [ ] Define status conditions for reconciliation\n34: - [ ] Implement status update logic\n35: - [ ] Add condition transitions (Ready, Pending, Failed)\n36: - [ ] Update observedGeneration tracking\n37: \n38: ## Phase 6: Error Handling & Backoff\n39: \n40: - [ ] Implement exponential backoff for retries\n41: - [ ] Configure max retries and backoff parameters\n42: - [ ] Distinguish transient vs permanent errors\n43: - [ ] Add reconciliation error metrics\n44: \n45: ## Phase 7: OwnerReference Management\n46: \n47: - [ ] Set OwnerReference on created child resources\n48: - [ ] Handle cascade deletion via garbage collector\n49: - [ ] Verify owner chain integrity\n50: \n51: ## Phase 8: Metrics & Observability\n52: \n53: - [ ] Expose reconciliation duration metrics\n54: - [ ] Add reconciliation error counters\n55: - [ ] Implement controller-runtime metrics\n56: - [ ] Add structured logging for reconciliation events\n57: \n58: ## Phase 9: Integration\n59: \n60: - [ ] Integrate with WorkloadManager service layer\n61: - [ ] Connect to AR-005/AR-006 handlers\n62: - [ ] Verify end-to-end reconciliation flow\n63: - [ ] Add integration tests\n64: \n65: ## Phase 10: Testing & Validation\n66: \n67: - [ ] Unit tests for reconciler logic\n68: - [ ] Integration tests with fake client\n69: - [ ] E2E tests with kind cluster\n70: - [ ] Verify metrics collection\n71: - [ ] Performance testing for concurrent reconciliations\n72: \n73: ## Checklist\n74: \n75: - [ ] Code follows Go best practices\n76: - [ ] All exported functions have documentation\n77: - [ ] Error handling is consistent with controller-runtime patterns\n78: - [ ] Configuration is externalized (resync period, backoff)\n79: - [ ] Tests cover happy path and error cases\n80: - [ ] Integration with existing WorkloadManager verified\n81: - [ ] Metrics and logging are documented\n82: - [ ] Finalizer behavior is tested\n\n(End of file - total 82 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007 Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1: Controller Foundation\n\n- [ ] Set up controller-runtime manager\n- [ ] Configure scheme with AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter types\n- [ ] Implement basic controller structure\n- [ ] Add health checks and metrics setup\n\n## Phase 2: Resource Watchers\n\n- [ ] Implement AgentRuntime resource watcher\n- [ ] Implement CodeInterpreter resource watcher\n- [ ] Configure event filters (generation, deletion timestamp)\n- [ ] Add watch predicates for relevant changes only\n\n## Phase 3: Reconcile Loop\n\n- [ ] Implement AgentRuntime reconciler\n- [ ] Implement CodeInterpreter reconciler","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/plan.md","time":{"start":1775853408843,"end":1775853408861}}}}
