{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853414871,"sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","part":{"id":"prt_d791ca54d001LNy5xLb7168Yjz","messageID":"msg_d791c929c001BKaE4I2LQogCXy","sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/tests.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/tests.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 Test Strategy\n2: \n3: ## Unit Tests\n4: \n5: ### Reconciler Tests\n6: \n7: - Test successful reconciliation of AgentRuntime\n8: - Test successful reconciliation of CodeInterpreter\n9: - Test finalizer addition on new resources\n10: - Test finalizer cleanup on deletion\n11: - Test status condition updates\n12: \n13: ### Error Handling Tests\n14: \n15: - Test exponential backoff behavior\n16: - Test max retry limit enforcement\n17: - Test transient vs permanent error classification\n18: - Test requeue on conflict errors\n19: \n20: ## Integration Tests\n21: \n22: ### Controller-Runtime Integration\n23: \n24: - Test watch events are received correctly\n25: - Test workqueue behavior\n26: - Test rate limiting configuration\n27: - Test scheme registration\n28: \n29: ### Resource Lifecycle Tests\n30: \n31: - Test create → reconcile → ready flow\n32: - Test update → reconcile flow\n33: - Test delete → finalizer → cleanup flow\n34: - Test OwnerReference propagation\n35: \n36: ## E2E Tests\n37: \n38: ### Kind Cluster Tests\n39: \n40: - Deploy controller to kind cluster\n41: - Create AgentRuntime CR and verify reconciliation\n42: - Create CodeInterpreter CR and verify reconciliation\n43: - Test deletion with finalizers\n44: - Verify metrics endpoint\n45: \n46: ## Test Coverage Goals\n47: \n48: - Reconciler logic: >= 80%\n49: - Error handling: >= 80%\n50: - Finalizer management: >= 80%\n51: - Status updates: >= 80%\n\n(End of file - total 51 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007 Test Strategy\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Reconciler Tests\n\n- Test successful reconciliation of AgentRuntime\n- Test successful reconciliation of CodeInterpreter\n- Test finalizer addition on new resources\n- Test finalizer cleanup on deletion\n- Test status condition updates\n\n### Error Handling Tests\n\n- Test exponential backoff behavior\n- Test max retry limit enforcement\n- Test transient vs permanent error classification\n- Test requeue on conflict errors\n\n## Integration Tests","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/tests.md","time":{"start":1775853414861,"end":1775853414870}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775853414874,"sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","part":{"id":"prt_d791ca087001zxlE7dCgaLgtrd","messageID":"msg_d791c929c001BKaE4I2LQogCXy","sessionID":"ses_286e3dfd6ffeQx7CUBHQTDRBo3","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-007 Design: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: **AR ID:** AR-007  \n6: **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n7: **Language:** Go  \n8: **Size:** Large  \n9: \n10: The K8s Reconciler Controller provides event-driven reconciliation for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs in the AgentCube system. It uses controller-runtime to watch resources, manage lifecycle transitions, and ensure cluster state matches desired state.\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Architecture\n15: \n16: ### High-Level Design\n17: \n18: ```\n19: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n20: │                     Kubernetes API Server                                   │\n21: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n22: │  │                     CRD Resources                                     │  │\n23: │  │  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐                     │  │\n24: │  │  │ AgentRuntime       │  │ CodeInterpreter    │                     │  │\n25: │  │  │ (watch)            │  │ (watch)            │                     │  │\n26: │  │  └────────┬───────────┘  └────────┬───────────┘                     │  │\n27: │  └───────────┼───────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┘  │\n28: │              │                       │                                       │\n29: └──────────────┼───────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────┘\n30:                │                       │\n31:                ▼                       ▼\n32: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n33: │                     Reconciler Controller                                   │\n34: │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n35: │  │                    Controller Manager                                   │ │\n36: │  │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n37: │  │  │                      Source (Watches)                             │ │ │\n38: │  │  │  ┌─────────────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────┐              │ │ │\n39: │  │  │  │ AgentRuntime Source │  │ CodeInterpreter Src │              │ │ │\n40: │  │  │  │ · Create Events     │  │ · Create Events     │              │ │ │\n41: │  │  │  │ · Update Events     │  │ · Update Events     │              │ │ │\n42: │  │  │  │ · Delete Events     │  │ · Delete Events     │              │ │ │\n43: │  │  │  └──────────┬──────────┘  └──────────┬──────────┘              │ │ │\n44: │  │  └─────────────┼────────────────────────┼─────────────────────────┘ │ │\n45: │  │                │                        │                           │ │\n46: │  │  ┌─────────────▼────────────────────────▼───────────────────────────┐ │ │\n47: │  │  │                      Work Queue                                   │ │ │\n48: │  │  │  · Rate limiting                                                   │ │ │\n49: │  │  │  · Retry with exponential backoff                                 │ │ │\n50: │  │  └────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n51: │  │                               │                                       │ │\n52: │  │  ┌────────────────────────────▼─────────────────────────────────────┐ │ │\n53: │  │  │                   Reconcile Loop                                  │ │ │\n54: │  │  │  ┌────────────────────┐  ┌────────────────────┐                │ │ │\n55: │  │  │  │ AgentRuntime       │  │ CodeInterpreter    │                │ │ │\n56: │  │  │  │ Reconciler         │  │ Reconciler         │                │ │ │\n57: │  │  │  └────────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘                │ │ │\n58: │  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │ │\n59: │  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n60: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n61: ```\n62: \n63: ---\n64: \n65: ## Components\n66: \n67: ### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## Interfaces\n72: \n73: ### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n74: \n75: ---\n76: \n77: ## Data Flow\n78: \n79: ### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n80: \n81: ---\n82: \n83: ## Error Handling\n84: \n85: ### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n86: \n87: ---\n88: \n89: ## Testing Strategy\n90: \n91: ### TBD - To be detailed during implementation\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ## References\n96: \n97: - [controller-runtime](https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime)\n98: - [AR-003: client-go Generated Code](../AR-003/)\n99: - [AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP Service Framework](../AR-004/)\n\n(End of file - total 99 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-007 Design: K8s Reconciler 控制器\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-007  \n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** Large  \n\nThe K8s Reconciler Controller provides event-driven reconciliation for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs in the AgentCube system. It uses controller-runtime to watch resources, manage lifecycle transitions, and ensure cluster state matches desired state.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Design\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     Kubernetes API Server                                   │","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-007/design.md","time":{"start":1775853414857,"end":1775853414872}}}}
